
Basic instructons:

1. Use the filters on the right hand side of the window to filter the
creatures you want to include in your generated encounter.

2.1. Generate a random encounter using the "Generate" button.
or
2.2. Generate a specific encounter by highlighting a creature type in the left
most panel and pressing "Add to Encounter". This generates an encounter with
the selected creature type.

3. Individual creatures can be added to the encounter by pressing the "Add"
button under the second panel. This opens a new window where specific creature
information can be entered.

4. The encounter panel can be sperated from the main window by pressing
"Popout" under the panel. This creates a new window of the current encounter.
